
Instalar:
https://nowardev.wordpress.com/2012/04/06/how-to-share-files-with-samba-under-kde-kubuntu-timeout-error-and-ect/

sudo apt-get install samba kdenetwork-filesharing libpam-winbind winbind



cómo poner password a samba:

 sudo smbpasswd -a 

allí poner una contraseña, ejemplo:

Jhon@139989

Me devuelve esto:

wachin@Dell-Inspiron-1750:~$  sudo smbpasswd -a 
[sudo] contraseña para wachin: 
New SMB password:
Retype new SMB password:
Added user root.
wachin@Dell-Inspiron-1750:~$ 

Sacarle respaldo a smb.conf

sudo cp /etc/samba/smb.conf /etc/samba/smb.conf.back

sudo gedit /etc/samba/smb.conf




visto en:
Linux Mint 17 Windows network setup - Linux Mint Community
https://community.linuxmint.com/tutorial/view/1861
